{"tid":891634,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"LIHKG 伺服器最新情況","createTime":"2018-11-06T09:36:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T07:45:34.000Z","uid":1,"like":66,"dislike":322,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"f5b68c6436a0e4a1e4e05dcbe93184a91d6aba6c","tid":891634,"uid":1,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:36:58.000Z","msg":"較早前因服務供應商出現問題使伺服器出現異常情況，我們已修復好大部份功能，並向各位受影響用戶致歉。<br />\n<br />\niOS 及 Android 用戶請重新啟動 LIHKG App 即可正常使用。部分用戶首次重啟時載入需時可能較長，以及「多媒體模式」有可能出現不能顯示縮圖的情況，目前正在搶修中。<br />\n<br />\n在此感謝各位耐心等候，我們會儘快完成維修工作，及持續監察伺服器狀態維持正常服務。<br />\n<br />\n如有進一步消息將於站務台及 Facebook 專頁發佈。"},{"pid":"f42f130e7aa3fdbc3fed7769c4141d3dcc774164","tid":891634,"uid":1249,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb0fb90e31e98ef853018be081f5b2935e4e4df","tid":891634,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ecee630dcc25e1c03f1d65f9b5d9d78321c1f7","tid":891634,"uid":17718,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a80eb961f9da2ccba2edc46f608e6a655d5d5a","tid":891634,"uid":7240,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:37:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2030940918748f0d0d052e257f80e169fc476c31","tid":891634,"uid":135445,"like":35,"dislike":26,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:37:27.000Z","msg":"連狗老母比狗屌"},{"pid":"de98b779734d2d341312a662a2ce005ec998a5b8","tid":891634,"uid":124824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:37:27